      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/604600189_18557096653037645_856426618731237988_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_p1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc5NDgzMzkwMzA5NDE1Mjc5NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxOC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=trEqXcs92tIQ7kNvwE6ZqNu&amp;_nc_oc=Adoy32ZzzBvh5jRY8HsKRrZPes8ey1Q6QW0JAg2oduF7DCF-K9iwZn3C4sPCwObeuhE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=uSQ0jIVix5hD3FUEddH4_g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzH2TvhxoZf4kzXBBA02lBnmaKF_FOZDLurrzxQyQbDuw&amp;oe=69CA2844" alt="Instagram billede fra @roisinmurphyofficial" /></p><p><strong>@roisinmurphyofficial</strong></p><p>This goes out to all the inspirational women in my life. Particularly you Elaine, Silvia, Viviana and Maria. Also to you Linda and my beautiful Mother, Rose. And my Nanna, who I miss more and more each passing year. Happy Christmas, I love you all so very deeply. ❤️🎄🤶🏼<br/>
#MillicentFawcett #strongwomen #christmas2025✨️</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/604600189_18557096653037645_856426618731237988_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_p1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc5NDgzMzkwMzA5NDE1Mjc5NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxOC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=trEqXcs92tIQ7kNvwE6ZqNu&amp;_nc_oc=Adoy32ZzzBvh5jRY8HsKRrZPes8ey1Q6QW0JAg2oduF7DCF-K9iwZn3C4sPCwObeuhE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=uSQ0jIVix5hD3FUEddH4_g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzH2TvhxoZf4kzXBBA02lBnmaKF_FOZDLurrzxQyQbDuw&amp;oe=69CA2844" alt="Instagram billede fra @roisinmurphyofficial" /></p><p><strong>@roisinmurphyofficial</strong></p><p>This goes out to all the inspirational women in my life. Particularly you Elaine, Silvia, Viviana and Maria. Also to you Linda and my beautiful Mother, Rose. And my Nanna, who I miss more and more each passing year. Happy Christmas, I love you all so very deeply. ❤️🎄🤶🏼<br/>
