ninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=uSQ0jIVix5hD3FUEddH4_g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfytLzbZ895tLxWiX3zZjdO1ZKzy4UwhugEfqeot0ueAWg&amp;oe=69CA223C" alt="Slide 3 fra @roisinmurphyofficial" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/543673105_18534277981037645_4862287392743046719_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s480x480_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcxNDQyNjI4NTIwNTI0OTQ4Mw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHg5NjAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=HAyRAbWXMNwQ7kNvwFqmxSB&amp;_nc_oc=Adoyxq-B_yvIHlIP0DZCUmpj9c9PN0z6U8YBRQ5vvKcIWZhNU8bPkbASOfXg33yB6es&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=uSQ0jIVix5hD3FUEddH4_g&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_Afx6NOkupXet00DIpnyVhrLFECFvYuwkbGeJczGblywHIA&amp;oe=69CA2717" alt="Slide 4 fra @roisinmurphyofficial" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (7 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@roisinmurphyofficial</strong></p><p>The best of them has passed 💔I sang for him twice. Once in Milan many years ago and once in Venice September ‘23 during the worst moment of my of my entire career. He was absolute gentleman and his team were warm and brilliant. A most surreal moment as my world was seeming to crumble and here I was staying for three days in a giant suite @venicevenicehotel looking out over the Grand Canal. And what a Dress! #GiorgioArmani you will be missed for everything you were 🖤🖤🖤@giorgioarmani</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DOMTXUWCFHd/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
